# Lychee link-checker ignore patterns
# Syntax: one pattern per line (glob or literal prefix)

# Localhost / 127.0.0.1 — never reachable in CI
http://localhost
http://127.0.0.1

# Placeholder / example URLs used in documentation code blocks
https://your-api-url.onrender.com
https://api.certi-vault.com

# Shield.io badges — flaky in CI but always resolve
https://img.shields.io

# Anchor-only links are checked by the markdown linter, not the link checker
#

# Docs paths that are directories (lychee resolves them as file links)
docs/api/
docs/architecture/
